        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    
               <h2 class="section-heading">Overview</h2>

             <p>Yeah the topic seems too great, football the most popular sports of the world and India the second most populated country. But together they dont go along well. India's greatest irony remains that we can reach the moon but just can't enter the fifa world cup.</p>

                    <img class="img-responsive" src="img/windows 10 game 1.jpg" alt="">
                    <span class="caption text-muted">Windows hopes to provide a richer gaming experience through enhanced graphics.</span>
                    
                <h2 class="section-heading">Football in India is like a minority without a reservation quota</h2>
          
                    
               <p>If you are an Indian only you know how hard it is to talk football. In a class of 40 hardly 5 to 10 students turn up and you will be fortunate enough to find someone who knows a bit more about cristiano or messi than you.</p>

                     <img class="img-responsive" src="img/windows 10 start menu.png" alt="">
                    <span class="caption text-muted">The all new and customisable start menu.</span>              

                    

                    
                    <h2 class="section-heading">I-league - A Mystery Yet To Be Solved</h2>

                       

                    <p>We can name the 11 players and the 5 substitutes of an England team but the mystery looms even on me when it comes to I-league. The total number of teams is still uncertain as of me leave alone the name of the players. We all have been through that phase where we would rather prefer learning from youtube or watchin videos of superstars of the game than learning from our local coach.  </p>


                     <img class="img-responsive" src="img/windows 10 virtual desktop.png" alt="">
                    <span class="caption text-muted">caption.</span>




                   
                    

                    <h2 class="section-heading">Incentives Taken Yet And Coming Ahead </h2>

                       
                    

<p>The ISL which has started from 2014 brings about some hope for the youngsters of the country as compared to the negligible stuff done previously to promote this world famous game in our country. New schemes are being undertaken and national camps being held for the youngsters so that they cultivate interest in themselves towards the game and one day india will too compete in the world cup.</p>


                      <img class="img-responsive" src="img/windows 10 edge.png" alt="">
                    <span class="caption text-muted">caption.</span>
 
                    
                    

               </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

